397
00:35:33.070 --> 00:35:35.580
Aku setuju. Mari kita coret.

398
00:35:35.580 --> 00:35:37.070
Apakah kau yakin?

399
00:35:37.470 --> 00:35:40.900
Aku akan memberi peringatan.

